videos.headline: Canes strike first on Perry's TD to Dallas
videos.description: Miami jumps out on top against Virginia on N'Kosi Perry's touchdown flip to DeeJay Dallas for the 17-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Canes strike first on Perry's TD to Dallas) 2019/10/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: The U breaks out turnover chain on fumble recovery
videos.description: Virginia RB Mike Hollins coughs up the football and is recovered by Miami's Trajan Bandy, who breaks out the turnover chain on the sideline.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (The U breaks out turnover chain on fumble recovery) 2019/10/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Miami safety ejected for targeting
videos.description: Virginia WR Hasise Dubois gets hit high by Amari Carter on an incomplete pass and Carter is ejected for targeting.
